2017/27/2017 - deleted param_lifetimecycles, so that we match what's in PROD.

2017/10/10: Imported newest version from PROD, which includes stand-alone properties for properties that used to only exist within Data Shapes.  (Jen)

2017/09/06: Change on properties for all parameters. DataChange must be on Value change must be on DataChange. Data Push must be Always
